8. Connect the Type-C cable to the camera unit.

Remember to ensure that the camera mounting position is within range of your home router for a strong and stable internet connection. Avoid facing the camera towards light sources or glass windows, as it may affect image performance. Clean the lens with a soft cloth from time to time for better image quality.

For more detailed instructions, refer to the "Camera Mounting" section in the manual.

To cancel your subscription, you can follow these steps based on the platform from which you created your account:

1.

**Google Play**: If you signed up via Google Play, you can cancel your subscription by going to the [Google Play Subscriptions](https://play.google.com/store/account/subscriptions) page. Search for "BIGVU Teleprompter & Video Captions" under your active subscriptions and choose to pause payments or cancel the subscription.

2.

**Apple App Store**: If you signed up through the Apple App Store, you can cancel your subscription by entering the subscription page in the app store. You can do this [here](https://apps.apple.com/account/subscriptions). Find "BIGVU Teleprompter" under your active subscriptions and click on it. Then, choose "Cancel Subscription" or "Cancel Free Trial" and confirm the cancellation.

3.

**BIGVU Website**: If you created your account directly on the BIGVU website, you can cancel your subscription by logging into [https://desk.bigvu.tv/](https://desk.bigvu.tv/). Click on the profile icon at the top right, select "Billing" from the dropdown menu, and choose "cancel subscription" in the billing screen.

Please note that after canceling your subscription, your plan will revert back to a free account, and your videos will be stored locally. If you have any further questions or need assistance, you can reach out to the support channel at support@bigvu.tv.

Sure! The process for requesting a refund for the BIGVU app depends on the platform from which you made the purchase. Here are the steps for each platform:

1. Apple - AppStore (iOS devices):
   - Go to [https://support.apple.com/en-il/HT204084](https://support.apple.com/en-il/HT204084) and connect with your Apple ID and password.
   - Select the option "Request a refund" and look for BIGVU under Purchases.
   - Once saved, you can check your refund status at [reportproblem.apple.com](https://idmsa.apple.com/IDMSWebAuth/signin?appIdKey=20379f32034f8867d352666ff2904d2152d5ff6843ee2db5ab5df863c14b1aef&path=%2F__logged_in%2Freportaproblem.apple.com&authResult=FAILED).

2. Google - Google PlayStore (Android devices):
   - Access [https://support.google.com/googleplay/answer/7205930](https://support.google.com/googleplay/answer/7205930) and click on "Request a refund".
   - Follow the steps to identify yourself and select the BIGVU app in your previous purchase to get a refund.

3. Web App - desk.bigvu.tv:
   - Please contact our support channel directly to request a refund at [support@bigvu.tv](mailto:support@bigvu.tv).

Remember that refunds for your subscription purchase are handled by the respective payment platform.

message:
To translate your video, follow these steps:

1. In the video maker, tap the three dots on the top right side of the screen.
2. Select "Translate Subtitles."
3. Tap the "Translate into another language" button.
4. On the Select Languages page, choose the original speech language and the language you want your subtitles to be translated to.
5. Press "Create Subtitles" once finalized.
6. Wait for the subtitles to generate. Once finished, you'll see the translated subtitles available.
7. Tap "Open" to edit the video using the chosen subtitle.

You can translate up to 20 languages in one click! Once you're done, you can download or share your video to your social media channels.

message:
To file nanny tax, you need to follow certain steps and fulfill your payroll tax responsibilities. Here is the relevant information from the documentation:

"You are responsible for federal employment taxes when you pay household workers as little as $1,000 in a calendar quarter or when you pay any individual employee age 18 or over $2,700 in a calendar year.

You have both Federal and State tax filing responsibilities. Federal employment taxes are reconciled with the household employerâ€™s annual Federal Income tax return. Your state may require quarterly unemployment tax filings, as well as reports and remittance of state income taxes withheld, if applicable. Employee wages are reported to the Social Security Administration. Your employee is due a W-2 form in January."

Based on this information, you need to file federal employment taxes with your annual Federal Income tax return. Additionally, you may have to file quarterly unemployment tax filings and report state income taxes withheld, depending on your state's requirements. You also need to provide your employee with a W-2 form in January.

Please note that this is a general overview, and it is recommended to consult with a tax professional or refer to the official IRS guidelines for detailed instructions on filing nanny tax.

speaker: assistant
message:
To deal with conflict between two members of staff, it is important to address the issue promptly and effectively. Here are some steps you can take based on the documentation:

1. **Address the conflict**: Schedule a meeting with both staff members involved to discuss the conflict. Introduce yourself and your role, and explain that your goal is to understand the situation and find a resolution.

2. **Listen actively**: During the meeting, actively listen to both staff members. Ask open-ended questions to understand their perspectives and the root causes of the conflict. Show genuine interest in their concerns and challenges.

3. **Remain neutral**: Avoid taking sides or expressing personal opinions about the individuals involved. Be neutral and focus on finding a solution that benefits the team as a whole.

4. **Facilitate communication**: Encourage open and respectful communication between the staff members. Help them express their thoughts and feelings constructively. Ask them to propose potential solutions to the conflict.

5. **Find common ground**: Look for areas of agreement or shared goals between the staff members. Emphasize the importance of teamwork and collaboration in achieving the organization's objectives.

6. **Mediate and negotiate**: If necessary, mediate the discussion and help the staff members negotiate a compromise or resolution. Encourage them to find mutually acceptable solutions and consider the impact on the team and the organization.

7. **Document the agreement**: Once a resolution is reached, summarize the agreed-upon solution in writing and have both staff members sign it. This helps ensure accountability and serves as a reference for future discussions.

Remember, conflict resolution is an ongoing process, and it may require follow-up meetings or additional support.

The 3 point turn technique is a method used to manage poor performance and help individuals achieve their goals. It involves a series of steps to review progress and make necessary adjustments. Here is an overview of the technique:

Phase one:
1. Schedule a meeting to review the individual's goal achievement plan.
2. Clarify that the purpose of the meeting is to assess progress towards goals.
3. Reiterate the agreements made and confirm the individual's understanding.
4. Discuss any discrepancies between the agreed goals and actual performance.
5. Ask the individual what they need to do to get back on track.
6. Offer support or assistance if needed.
7. Allow the individual to share any additional concerns or issues.
8. Summarize the new agreement in writing and have both parties sign it.

The technique is effective in addressing goal-related issues and reminding individuals of the importance of goal achievement.

To go about exiting your business, it's important to have a clear understanding of your goals and motivations for the sale. Here are some tips from the documentation:

1. Start with the end in mind: Define your goals and what you want to achieve from the sale. This will help you make informed decisions throughout the process.

2. Take care with brokers and corporate finance houses: While professional advisors are essential, remember that they have their own interests. Get references from their recent clients and don't rely solely on them to find buyers for your business.

3. Do due diligence on the purchasing company: It's important to research and understand the company that is interested in buying your business. This will help you make an informed decision and ensure a smooth transition.

4. Be open, honest, and transparent: Maintain open communication with potential buyers and be transparent about the details of your business. This will build trust and facilitate a smoother sale process.

5. Be prepared for allegiances to swap to the buyer: During the sale process, be aware that some of your team members may align themselves with the buyer. Be prepared for this possibility and manage the transition effectively.

Remember, these are just a few tips to help you navigate the process of exiting your business. It's always recommended to seek professional advice and guidance tailored to your specific situation. These factors include rarity value, niche market, good intellectual property (IP), positive cash generation, reliable recurring revenue, and multiple revenue streams. On the other hand, you should be cautious of businesses that have risks such as litigation, vulnerability to new legislation, shareholder disputes, vulnerable supply chains, and dependence on a few customers, people, or offerings.

By evaluating these factors, you can identify businesses that align with your strategic goals and have the potential for growth and profitability. It's important to conduct due diligence on potential acquisitions and assess their fit with your existing business and industry. If you're struggling with staff motivation, there are several steps you can take to address the issue. Here's what the documentation suggests:

1. Engage in open communication: Talk to your staff members and listen to their concerns and ideas. Show genuine interest in their goals and challenges.

2. Set clear expectations: Clearly communicate your expectations and goals for the team. Make sure everyone understands their roles and responsibilities.

3. Recognize and appreciate achievements: Acknowledge and appreciate the efforts and achievements of your staff members. This can be done through verbal recognition, rewards, or other forms of appreciation.

4. Provide opportunities for growth and development: Offer training, learning opportunities, and career development programs to help your staff members grow and enhance their skills.

5. Foster a positive work environment: Create a positive and supportive work environment where employees feel valued, respected, and motivated. Encourage teamwork and collaboration.

6. Lead by example: Be a role model for your staff members. Demonstrate enthusiasm, passion, and a strong work ethic. Show them that you are committed to their success.

Remember, motivation is a complex issue, and different strategies may work for different individuals. It's important to tailor your approach based on the specific needs and preferences of your staff members.

speaker: assistant
message:
For a company that is growing and expanding, I would advise the following:

1. **Recruit the right people**: As your business grows, it's crucial to have capable managers who can drive business success. Avoid the temptation to hire people who are less capable than yourself. Instead, focus on recruiting individuals who can contribute to the growth and success of your company. [^Recruit-the-right-people]

2. **Develop, don't recruit, megastars**: Rather than solely relying on external recruitment, consider developing your existing employees into megastars. By investing in their growth and providing them with a great work environment, you can attract top talent within their social networks and increase their investment in the firm. [^Utilise-your-existing-employees]

3. **Keep your product range focused**: As you expand, it's important to maintain focus on your core products or services. Avoid the temptation to diversify too quickly or take on too many projects. By keeping your product range focused, you can ensure quality and better meet the needs of your target market. [^Keep-your-product-range-focused]

4. **Invest in infrastructure and specialist skills**: As your business grows, invest in the necessary infrastructure and specialist skills to support that growth. This may include upgrading technology systems, expanding your physical space, or hiring experts in specific areas. By investing in infrastructure and specialist skills, you can ensure that your business can handle the demands of expansion. [^Invest-in-infrastructure-and-specialist-skills]

5. **Watch the cash cost of growth**: While growth is exciting, it's important to keep a close eye on the financial implications. Monitor your cash flow and ensure that your growth is sustainable. Avoid overextending yourself financially and make strategic decisions that align with your long-term goals. [^Watch-the-cash-cost-of-growth]

6. **Create excellence by not accepting the average**: Strive for excellence in all aspects of your business. Set high standards and hold yourself and your team accountable. By not accepting mediocrity, you can differentiate your company from competitors and build a reputation for quality and excellence. [^Create-excellence-by-not-accepting-the-average]

7. **Work towards long-term, not just short-term success**: While it's important to achieve short-term goals, don't lose sight of the bigger picture. Creating a positive work environment, offering work/life balance, and providing benefits that prioritize employee well-being can contribute to employee happiness.

2. **Productivity**: Engaged employees are generally more motivated and aim to produce great results for their employers. When employees feel connected to their work and have a sense of purpose, they are more likely to be productive and contribute to the success of the organization.

3. **Collaboration**: In a company with a strong positive culture, employees feel closely connected to their colleagues and work together more effectively. Encouraging collaboration and fostering a sense of teamwork can enhance employee engagement and retention.

4. **Recruit for company culture**: When hiring new employees, it is important to consider their fit with the company culture. As a growing business, new roles may emerge that could be an ideal fit for these candidates. Maintaining a talent pool can help in quickly filling positions with qualified individuals.

SQream leverages the power of GPUs for efficient data analysis without the need for intermediate steps. By utilizing the raw computing power of GPUs, data can be loaded and analyzed immediately. Unlike traditional data warehouses that rely on a fixed set of resources, SQream's flexible solution can allocate resources dynamically to handle varying workloads. This includes utilizing available CPU, GPU, RAM, and storage resources, with a focus on maintaining a balance between CPU and GPU operations for optimal performance. message: How does SQream accelerate data processing?

welcome_message:
ðŸš€ Welcome to SQream! Leverage SQL on GPU to reduce analytics costs and increase performance!
Would you like to ask me about data challenges, watch a short demo or schedule a chat with our data solution experts? 
<sub>(To find more about our privacy policy, [click here](https://sqream.com/privacy-policy))</sub>
speaker: assistant
message:
SQream's unique GPU-acceleration combines two types of parallelism: between separate nodes (similar to any other MPP); and on a single GPU chip (MPP-on-chip). A single node can also host multiple GPUs to increase concurrency even further. This allows the capabilities of every individual compute unit to be logically and rapidly multiplied without installing any additional nodes. It also means that each GPU can work simultaneously, rather than serially, on several different tasks. SQream accelerates data processing end to end, from data preparation to insights, with its unique multi-level GPU parallelizing technology, decoupled storage and compute, and rapid metadata standardization.

message: Before each annual meeting, the Board of Directors may appoint a committee of three members who shall nominate candidates for the Board. The names of the candidates shall be submitted on or before thirty (30) days before the election. Members may submit names of candidates other than those submitted by the nominating committee at least sixty (60) days prior to the election. Unless such names are submitted, either by the nominating committee or by the members, no person shall be elected whose name is not submitted unless NO nominations are made, in which event the names of candidates shall be submitted at the election by the members.

The owner's vote is counted towards the majority of owners, which is defined as those voting owners holding fifty-one percent (51%) of the Common Interest. So, "by a vote of the association" means that the decision is made based on the votes of the majority of owners.

message: The property is required to have insurance that covers at least all of the Common Elements, as well as the improvements, installations, and fixtures in each Unit. The policy should also include comprehensive public liability insurance covering the entire Condominium Project with limits not less than $1,000,000 for personal injury and/or property damage arising out of a single occurrence.

message:
To add subtitles to your video using BIGVU, you can follow these steps:

1. In the video maker, tap the three dots on the top right side of the screen.
2. Select "Translate Subtitles."
3. Tap the "Translate into another language" button.
4. Choose the original speech language and the language you want your subtitles to be translated to.
5. Press "Create Subtitles" once finalized.
6. Wait for the subtitles to generate.
7. Once finished, you'll see the translated subtitles available.
8. Tap "Open" to edit the video using the chosen subtitle.

You can translate up to 20 languages in one click! This allows you to reach a global audience by adding captions in different languages.

message:
H2Neo and H2Max are types of ships used for the transportation of compressed hydrogen. They differ in their cargo size and power requirements. H2Neo has a cargo size of 430 tonnes of H2 (gross) and 415 tonnes of H2 (net), with a fuel cell size of 15.6 MW. The capital costs for H2Neo are estimated at 175 million US dollars, with operating and maintenance costs of 5.1 million US dollars per annum.

On the other hand, H2Max has a larger cargo size of 2,000 tonnes of H2 (gross) and 1,930 tonnes of H2 (net), with a fuel cell size of 27.0 MW. The capital costs for H2Max are higher, estimated at 400 million US dollars, with operating and maintenance costs of 6.7 million US dollars per annum.

message: DCO stands for OpenVPN Data Channel Offload. It is a new development introduced by OpenVPN that improves the speed and performance for its users. DCO implements a Linux kernel module that handles the OpenVPN data channel, allowing data traffic to be processed within the kernel space instead of being transferred between the user and kernel space. This optimization reduces latency and improves data transfer speeds. Additionally, DCO incorporates multi-threading for encryption, further enhancing the speed of data transfer. Overall, DCO aims to eliminate bottlenecks and provide faster and more efficient communication for OpenVPN users.

speaker: assistant
message: A profile in the context of OpenVPN refers to a connection profile or a configuration file (.ovpn text file) that contains the directives, parameters, and certificates required to establish a client-server VPN connection. It includes information such as server addresses, ports, authentication details, and other settings necessary for the VPN connection. There are different types of profiles, such as user-locked profiles that require specific user credentials, auto-login profiles that do not require credentials, and server-locked profiles that require credentials for any valid user on the server. Profiles can be obtained by installing OpenVPN Connect with a bundled profile, importing a profile from a file, or importing a profile from a URL.

message: how do i backup access server

welcome_message:
Hello! I'm agent aibot-openvpn.
I'm here to answer any questions you have, or maybe you'd rather choose a question others are asking me?
[more about me >](action/profile)
speaker: assistant
message:
To backup Access Server in OpenVPN Connect, you can use the following commands with root privileges:

```bash
which apt > /dev/null 2>&1 && apt -y install sqlite3
which yum > /dev/null 2>&1 && yum -y install sqlite
cd /usr/local/openvpn_as/etc/db
[ -e config.db ] && sqlite3 config.db .dump > ../../config.db.bak
[ -e certs.db ] && sqlite3 certs.db .dump > ../../certs.db.bak
[ -e userprop.db ] && sqlite3 userprop.db .dump > ../../userprop.db.bak
[ -e log.db ] && sqlite3 log.db .dump > ../../log.db.bak
[ -e config_local.db ] && sqlite3 config_local.db .dump > ../../config_local.db.bak
[ -e cluster.db ] && sqlite3 cluster.db .dump > ../../cluster.db.bak
[ -e clusterdb.db ] && sqlite3 clusterdb.db .dump > ../../clusterdb.db.bak
[ -e notification.db ] && sqlite3 notification.db .dump > ../../notification.db.bak
cp ../as.conf ../../as.conf.bak
```

These commands will create backup files of the Access Server configuration files in the `/usr/local/openvpn_as/` directory. The backup files will have the extension `.bak` and contain all the necessary information for your OpenVPN Access Server installation.

Please note that these backup files contain sensitive information, so make sure to store them securely.

For more details, you can refer to the [Configuration Database Management And Backups](https://openvpn.net/vpn-server-resources/configuration-database-management-and-backups/) documentation.

message: how do i setup site-to-site routing

welcome_message:
Hello! I'm agent aibot-openvpn.
I'm here to answer any questions you have, or maybe you'd rather choose a question others are asking me?
[more about me >](action/profile)
speaker: assistant
message:
To set up site-to-site routing in OpenVPN Connect, you need to configure the settings in the Admin Web UI of Access Server. Here are the steps:

1. Sign in to the Admin Web UI for your Access Server.
2. Click on "Configuration" and then "VPN Settings".
3. Under "Routing" and "Should VPN clients have access to private subnets (non-public networks on the server side)?", select "Yes, using Routing".
4. Click on "Specify the private subnets to which all clients should be given access (one per line)".
5. Enter the network subnet where your Access Server is located.
6. Click on "User Management" and then "User Permissions".
7. Enter a new username for your OpenVPN client.
8. Click on "Allow auto-login" and then "More Settings".
9. Select "Local" for the Auth method.
10. Enter a new password.
11. Set "Configure VPN Gateway" to "Yes".
12. Enter the subnet of the remote network of the OpenVPN client into the box for "Allow client to act as VPN gateway for these client-side subnets".

These steps will configure the site-to-site routing in OpenVPN Connect. Remember to adjust the settings according to your specific subnets and networks.

For more information, you can refer to the [Tutorial: Create a site-to-site network with Access Server](https://openvpn.net/as-docs/tutorials/tutorial--site-to-site-network.html) documentation.

speaker: assistant
message:
OpenVPN Access Server provides several examples of post-auth scripts that you can use to extend the authentication capabilities. Here are some examples:

1. **PAS-only custom authentication script**: You can implement an entirely new custom authentication method in Access Server using a properly configured post-auth script. This script allows you to handle authentication entirely within the script itself. [More information](https://openvpn.net/vpn-server-resources/using-auth_null-for-custom-authentication/)

2. **Hardware address checking script**: Access Server supports hardware address checking by loading a post-auth script that requires the correct hardware address at connection time. This script can record and check hardware addresses for first-time connections or run in manual mode where approved hardware addresses are manually added on the server. [More information](https://openvpn.net/vpn-server-resources/access-server-post-auth-script-host-checking/)

3. **LDAP group mapping script**: You can automate the assignment of users to Access Server groups based on their LDAP group membership using the LDAP group mapping script. This script allows you to define rules that automatically assign users in specified LDAP groups to specified Access Server groups during authentication. [More information](https://openvpn.net/vpn-server-resources/access-server-post-auth-script-ldap-group-mapping/)

4. **RADIUS group mapping script**: Similar to the LDAP group mapping script, the RADIUS group mapping script allows you to automate the assignment of users to Access Server groups based on their RADIUS group membership. This script reads and uses RADIUS properties to apply group membership and other settings. [More information](https://openvpn.net/vpn-server-resources/access-server-post-auth-script-ldap-group-mapping/)

These examples demonstrate how you can customize the authentication process in OpenVPN Access Server using post-auth scripts. For more details and documentation on each script, please refer to the provided links.

To assign a static IP address in OpenVPN Access Server, you can follow the steps outlined in the Access Server documentation.

1. Log in to the Access Server Admin Web UI.
2. Go to the "VPN Settings" page.
3. Under the "Network Settings" section, click on "IP Address Network".
4. Select the option to "Use a static IP address".
5. Enter the desired static IP address in the provided field.
6. Save the changes.

For more detailed instructions and information, you can refer to the Access Server documentation on assigning a static IP address.

[Access Server Documentation - Assigning a Static IP Address](https://openvpn.net/vpn-server-resources/)

To get an auto-login profile in OpenVPN Access Server, you need to follow these steps:

1. Sign in to the Admin Web UI.
2. Click on "User Permissions" and then "User Management".
3. Find the user from the list and check the "Allow Auto-login" option.
4. Click "Save Settings and Update Running Server".

Once the auto-login permission is granted, the user can download and import the auto-login connection profile from the Client Web UI. They can then set the launch options in OpenVPN Connect to automatically connect to the VPN at startup.

welcome_message:

[more about me >](action/profile)
speaker: assistant
message:
To safely date someone with Complex PTSD (CPTSD), it's important to approach the relationship with patience, understanding, and knowledge about their individual needs. Here are some tips:

1. Educate yourself: Learn about CPTSD and its effects on relationships. Understanding their triggers and symptoms can help you provide appropriate support.

2. Open communication: Foster open and empathetic communication. Listen without judgment, validate their emotions, and be willing to learn about their triggers. Establish boundaries and create safe spaces for them to express their feelings.

3. Recognize PTSD episodes: Learn to recognize the signs of a PTSD episode, such as emotional withdrawal, sudden anger, or physical manifestations. Remind them of grounding techniques and reassure them of their safety during these episodes.

4. Emotional support: Provide emotional support by listening, expressing empathy, and offering reassurance. Encourage self-care practices and engage in activities that promote relaxation and connection.

5. Respect personal space: Respect their personal space and avoid startling them. Be understanding if they need time alone or if they have specific boundaries.

6. Crisis plan: Work together on a crisis plan to effectively deal with triggers and difficult times. This can help both of you navigate challenging situations.

Remember, every individual is unique, so it's important to communicate openly and adapt to their specific needs. If needed, encourage them to seek professional help from a mental health professional specializing in trauma.

message: EXIM Bank Agricultural University, Bangladesh (EBAUB) is a specialized private university in Bangladesh that focuses on providing quality education in the field of agriculture. It aims to raise the level of education and address agricultural problems in the northern part of Bangladesh. EBAUB offers international standard education programs and conducts agricultural research at a reasonable cost to students. The university has qualified and experienced teaching faculty, state-of-the-art labs, equipment, and training facilities. EBAUB's vision is to be recognized as a flagship research-led university known for excellence in teaching, research, and service to local, national, and international communities. The university also emphasizes the importance of drive and passion in students to help them achieve their dreams.

- GPA 10 (With 4th Subject): BDT 2,80,900

welcome_message:

I'm here to answer any questions you have, or maybe you'd rather choose a question others are asking me?
[more about me >](action/profile)
speaker: assistant
message:
To create manual orders in Drupal, follow these steps:

1. Go to the Orders page in Drupal.
2. On the left-hand side, you can search for orders using various criteria such as customer name, website, product, phone number, email address, address, and more.
3. Choose your preferred method of searching for the customer, such as by phone number.
4. Once you have located the customer, click on their name or order number to access their order details.
5. Review the order with the customer to ensure accuracy.
6. Scroll to the top right of the order view page and click on "Payments."
7. Click on "Add Payment" to proceed with the payment process.
8. Select the appropriate payment option, such as credit card or pay check.
9. If the customer does not have a card on file, you will need to add a new one by selecting the credit card option and entering the card details.
10. If the customer has a card on file, the last 4 digits of the card will be displayed. For security reasons, ask the customer to provide the last 4 digits of the card.
11. Confirm the payment details and the total amount before processing the payment.

Please note that these steps are based on the information provided in the documentation.

welcome_message:
Hello! I'm agent l-8523.
I'm here to answer any questions you have, or maybe you'd rather choose a question others are asking me?
[more about me >](action/profile)
speaker: assistant
message:
To place an order, follow these steps:

1. Access the Orders page in the Online Store.
2. Search for the customer by using their username, email address, or phone number.
3. Once you find the customer, assign the order to them.
4. Fill in the billing information, including the address. Confirm that the address is correct or add a new one if needed.
5. Add the items to the order by clicking "Add new order item" and typing the item's name or SKU number.
6. Review the order details, including any discounts or coupons, salesperson's name, and tags.
7. Proceed to the payment section and select the payment method.
8. Complete the payment process. You can verify the payment status on the Payments page.
9. Finally, scroll down to the bottom right of the view page and click "Place Order" to finalize the order.

Note: The placed order will automatically go into manual review as part of the fraud protection program. You can approve the order from there.

message: How can you honor a BOGO deal if the customer forgets to add the code?

welcome_message:
Hello! I'm agent l-8523.
I'm here to answer any questions you have, or maybe you'd rather choose a question others are asking me?
[more about me >](action/profile)
speaker: assistant
message:
If the customer forgets to add the BOGO code, you can still honor the deal. Here's what you need to do:

1. Create a new order.
2. Add the items for the BOGO deal.
3. Add an adjustment of type "Custom" with the label "BOGO add on" and subtract the amount the customer paid on the original order.
4. Exclude website promotions.
5. Add the salesperson.
6. Tag the order as "BOGO".
7. Confirm the amount and last 4 digits of the card with the customer.

The total of the new order should be the amount that was discounted from the original order.

Hello! I'm agent l-8523.

[more about me >](action/profile)
speaker: assistant
message:
To masquerade as a customer, you can follow these steps:

1. Open an incognito tab in Google Chrome.
2. Login to the store.
3. Open the People/Customers tab.
4. Search for the customer by their email.
5. In the dropdown menu under operations, choose "Masquerade as."
6. You will now be logged in as the customer and can see what the customer sees.

Please note that it's important to do this in a private browsing window to avoid logging yourself out completely.

[more about me >](action/profile)
speaker: assistant
message: If an order is shipped to the wrong address, you should follow the reshipment process. You need to make a note of the original order number and the reason for reshipping. If there is an intercom ticket, you should post the URL to the conversation in the comments box. Additionally, if you send a return label, make a note of why you are sending it on the order. It is important to follow up on the RMA (Return Merchandise Authorization) to ensure the customer receives either a store credit, exchange, or refund. Always push for store credit or exchange first.

Hello! I'm agent l-8523.

[more about me >](action/profile)
speaker: assistant
message:
If the customer forgets to add the BOGO code, you can still honor the deal. Here's what you need to do:

1. Create a new order.
2. Add the items for the BOGO deal.
3. Add a custom adjustment for the BOGO add-on and subtract the amount the customer paid on the original order.
4. Exclude website promotions.
5. Add the salesperson.
6. Tag the order as "BOGO."
7. Confirm the amount and last 4 digits of the card with the customer.

The total of the new order should be the amount that was discounted from the original order.

message:
To create a return, follow these steps:

1. Have the customer send a photo of the unopened items they wish to return.
2. Once you have the photo, send the return label to the customer.
3. Refund the customer once the warehouse logs the returned items into the return log.
4. Make sure all items are logged into the return log by the warehouse before issuing a refund.
5. If a customer has a bad reaction to gummies, request photos of the lot number.
6. If a customer sends back an empty jar, they will not be provided a refund or in-store credit.
7. Tag the order with "badreaction" if necessary.

Please note that all items need to be logged into the return log by the warehouse before refunding. If you don't see it on the log but it has been delivered, please ask the warehouse chat if they received it back.

To use the RMA log, you can follow these steps:

1. Open the RMA log by navigating to [https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/ luZs3UMDWOipfUKQivbYzBYzpXxZLqXLGsEA9j9IVLmA/edit#gid=0](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1uZs3UMDWOipfUKQivbYzBYzpXxZLqXLGsEA9j9lVLmA/edit%23gid=0).

3. If you can't find the return by order number, you can try searching by RMA number or customer's name.
4. If you still can't find the return, check for the date when it was received back and ask the warehouse if they have it.

Please note that the RMA log is a tool to track returns, and you can use it to locate specific returns based on different search criteria.

message:
To export all your scripts from BIGVU, you can follow these steps:

1. Login to [desk.bigvu.tv](http://desk.bigvu.tv/) and click on your Profile photo.
2. Select "Profile" from the dropdown menu.
3. On your Profile Page, scroll down and look for "Export All My Data" under the "Preferences" section.
4. Click on "Export All My Data" to initiate the export process.
5. You will receive a link to a downloadable zip file containing all your BIGVU data, including your scripts.

Please note that the download link expires after 7 days.

message: What are some examples of prohibited content?

welcome_message:
Hello! I'm agent aircall-extension-reach.
I'm here to answer any questions you have, or maybe you'd rather choose a question others are asking me?
[more about me >](action/profile)
speaker: assistant
message:
Prohibited content includes but is not limited to:

- Hate speech, harassment, incitement to terrorism, exploitative, and abusive content.
- Phishing and fraudulent messages.
- Malicious content, such as malware or viruses.
- Any content that is designed to intentionally evade carrier filtering (such as spreading similar messages across different numbers - also known as "snowshoeing").
- Deceptive marketing, pyramid or multi-level marketing, high-risk financial services or activities, gambling, "get rich" schemes.

For more information, please refer to the documentation on [Prohibited content and use cases](knowledge.txt#prohibited-content-and-use-cases).

message:
To contact the sales team, you can reach out to the Customer Success Team by email:

- APAC: success-apac@aircall.io
- EMEA: success@aircall.io
- NA: successteam@aircall.io

You can also submit a ticket through the Aircall Support Portal. Here's how:

1. Go to https://support.aircall.io/hc/en-gb and select "Submit or View Requests."
2. Log in with your Aircall credentials.
3. Select "Contact Us" and then "Submit a request."
4. Choose "Billing, Invoicing, and Payments" as your contact reason.
5. Complete the form with as much detail as possible.

Please note that the sales team does not handle requests regarding subscription management. For assistance with plan, contract amendments, billing frequency changes, and other subscription-related inquiries, it's best to contact the Customer Success Team.

welcome_message:
Hello! I'm agent aircall-extension-reach.
I'm here to answer any questions you have, or maybe you'd rather choose a question others are asking me?
[more about me >](action/profile)
speaker: assistant
message:
To use the Aircall API, you need to follow these steps:

1. Authenticate to the API: You must be a paying customer of Aircall Surveys to use the API. Instructions to authenticate to the API are listed in the documentation introduction [here](https://support.aircall.io/hc/en-gb/articles/11412749023645-How-to-use-the-Aircall-Surveys-API).

2. Use the API for various purposes: The Aircall API allows you to connect other applications with your Aircall application. You can retrieve call information, link your user provisioning software to the Aircall database, or manage your Aircall contacts list. There are three different ways of using the API: synchronizing your own data with your Aircall account, customizing your call workflows, or integrating your solution and becoming an Aircall partner.

For further information on how to start using the Aircall API, you can refer to the documentation [here](https://support.aircall.io/hc/en-gb/articles/10375355327517-Aircall-API-and-Webhooks).

[more about me >](action/profile)
speaker: assistant
message:
The documentation provides guidance on troubleshooting Salesforce integration issues. Here are some key points to consider:

- The integration is set up at the number level, so make sure you have the required Aircall subscription and the necessary plan for your CRM.
- Ensure that each user connected to Aircall and Salesforce has the same email address in both systems.
- Check if the Admin user is the same in both Aircall and Salesforce during installation.
- Avoid making custom fields mandatory in your integration, as it can cause issues with call logging.
- If you've checked these requirements and still experience issues, collect call examples and submit a ticket to the support team for further investigation.

For more detailed troubleshooting steps, you can refer to the [Integrations Troubleshooting Guide](https://support.aircall.io/hc/en-gb/articles/10375355878813-Integrations-Troubleshooting-Guide).

message:
To replace the blower assembly, follow these steps:

1. Remove the blower skid bar by removing the front and rear mounting bolts from the skid bar (underneath the blower) and removing the bolt connecting the blower housing to the skid bar.
2. Remove the blower belt tightener idler arm assembly by removing the pivot bolt.
3. Remove two bolts mounting the blower housing to the frame.
4. Lower the blower assembly straight down out of the chassis frame and remove.

Please note that these instructions are for a specific model (MS). Make sure to refer to the appropriate section in the documentation for your specific model.

welcome_message:

[more about me >](action/profile)
speaker: assistant
message:
To change the PTO gearbox oil, you can follow these steps:

1. Thoroughly clean the exterior of the transmission housing before servicing.
2. Using a 1/4" hex wrench, remove the plug located approximately 2" (50 mm) from the bottom on the back side of each transaxle allowing the oil to drain.
3. To remove the remainder of the oil below the plug, use an oil suction gun.
4. Reinstall drain plugs.
5. Remove and replace the oil filters using a 3/8" hex wrench.
6. Using an oil suction gun, remove all oil in the reservoirs.
7. Fill the transaxles with 20W-50 oil through the opening where the elbows were. Fill up to the opening.

Please refer to the "Changing Gearbox Oil" section in the documentation for more detailed instructions and illustrations.

Walker Manufacturing company will repair or replace the defective part without charge. The warranty does not cover defects caused by normal wear, accidents, improper maintenance, improper use or abuse of the product, alterations, or failure to follow the instructions in the Operator's Manual for operation and maintenance. The warranty does not cover the Kohler Engine and Battery, as they are warranted separately by their respective manufacturers. Extended warranties are offered for certain powertrain components. [more about me >](action/profile)
speaker: assistant
message:
To adjust the tracking on the mower, follow these steps:

1. Sit in the seat and start the engine.
2. With the Forward Speed Control (FSC) in the NEUTRAL-PARK position, check for forward movement of either drive wheel. If either wheel moves backward, refer back to the Neutral Function Adjustment - Step 3 and readjust.
3. Tighten the steering lever adjustment nut on the side of the mower with the wheel moving forward until wheel movement stops.
4. Check for straight ground track on a level surface by setting the FSC at several different speeds and observing if the mower moves in a straight line. You can use a cement joint or other line on the ground for reference.
5. Make any necessary adjustments to ensure straight ground tracking.

Please refer to the documentation for more detailed instructions and illustrations.

1. Remove the mower deck. Refer to Deck Installation in the Set-Up Section and reverse the procedure to remove the deck.
2. Remove the blower faceplate by removing six (6) 1/4-20 nuts.

4. Lower the blower assembly straight down out of the chassis frame and remove.

message:
To check the oil level in the gearbox and maintain it, follow these steps:

1. Clean the area around the gearbox cover plates to prevent contaminants from entering the gearcase.
2. Remove the screws securing the cover plates on the gearbox.
3. Check the level of lubricant in the gearbox. If the lubricant is low, add SAE E.P. (Extreme Pressure) 80W-90 gear lube until the oil level is up to the horizontal shaft in the gearbox.
4. If the gearbox is completely drained of oil, approximately 5 fl. oz. of oil is required to refill the gear drive assembly.
5. Since the gearboxes are connected as a unit by connector tubes, it is necessary to add oil slowly and allow a few minutes for the oil to flow throughout the assembly and the oil level to stabilize before reassembly.
6. IMPORTANT: Do not overfill the gearbox. Overfilling with oil can cause excessive pressure and result in oil leaks.
7. Check the condition of the cover gasket and replace it if worn or damaged.
8. Reinstall the gearbox cover plates and torque the screws to the specified torque value.

Please note that the specific instructions may vary depending on the model and type of gearbox. It is recommended to refer to the owner's manual or consult a professional for detailed instructions for your specific gearbox.

To replace the PTO belt on the MT model, follow these steps:

1. Remove the two mounting bolts holding the PTO belt guide in place and loosen the front mounting bolts of the PTO actuator assembly. Remove the belt guide and the nuts on the front of the brake band.
2. Unhook the spring and unbolt the actuator clevis attached to the PTO gearbox assembly. Pull the gearbox assembly to the rear and remove the belt.
3. Install the new PTO drive belt by reversing the removal procedure.

For more detailed instructions and illustrations, please refer to the "PTO Drive and Ground Drive Belt Removal" section in the Service Instructions of the documentation.

message:
To remove the blower on a MT25i, follow these steps:

1. Remove the mower deck. Refer to the Deck Installation section in the Set-Up instructions and reverse the procedure to remove the deck.
2. Remove the blower faceplate by removing the six (6) 1/4-20 nuts.
3. Remove the blower assembly from the chassis by removing the front and rear mounting bolts from the blower skid bar (located underneath the blower) and the bolt connecting the blower housing to the skid bar.
4. Remove the two (2) bolts mounting the blower housing to the frame and the bolt mounting the scrubber brake assembly on the blower housing.
5. Remove the scrubber brake assembly and roll the blower drive belt off of the blower pulley.
6. Lower the blower assembly straight down out of the chassis frame and remove it.

Please note that these instructions are specific to the MT25i model. If you have a different model, please provide the model number for more accurate instructions.

message: Before the commencement of erection of any floor units, all temporary propping should be in place, adjusted to the correct levels allowing for any required cambers, and fully braced. This is to ensure that the temporary propping provides full support for all construction loads, including the full self-weight of the completed floor system and possible local concentrations of load during construction, unless specifically noted otherwise. Additionally, props should be vertical and braced to prevent side-sway of the whole assembly and the buckling of individual props.

welcome_message:

[more about me >](action/profile)
speaker: assistant
message:
To create a repository in GitHub, you can follow these steps:

Step 1: Go to the GitHub website and log in to your account.

Step 2: Click on the "+" icon in the top right corner of the page and select "New repository" from the dropdown menu.

Step 3: Enter a name for your repository. Choose a descriptive name that reflects the purpose of your project.

Step 4: Optionally, you can add a description for your repository to provide more information about it.

Step 5: Choose whether you want your repository to be public or private. Public repositories are visible to everyone, while private repositories are only accessible to you and collaborators you invite.

Step 6: Select the option to initialize your repository with a README file. This is useful for providing an overview or instructions for your project.

Step 7: You can also add a .gitignore file and choose a license for your repository, depending on your project's needs.

Step 8: Finally, click on the "Create repository" button to create your repository.

Once your repository is created, you can start adding files, making changes, and collaborating with others using Git commands or GitHub's web interface.

message: What is the data loading process into SQream?

welcome_message:
ðŸš€ Welcome to SQream! Leverage SQL on GPU to reduce analytics costs and increase performance!
Would you like to ask me about data challenges, watch a short demo or schedule a chat with our data solution experts? 
<sub>(To find more about our privacy policy, [click here](https://sqream.com/privacy-policy))</sub>
speaker: assistant
message:
The data loading process into SQream involves ingesting data from a variety of sources and locations. This can be done by executing the INSERT statement using a client driver, or by executing the COPY FROM statement to ingest data from foreign tables, including local filesystems, network filesystems, Amazon S3, and HDFS. SQream supports loading files in formats such as Text (CSV, TSV, and PSV), Parquet, ORC, Avro, and JSON. Additionally, the process includes chunking, metadata tagging, and automatic adaptive compression to prepare the data for analytics.

message: What role does data preprocessing and wrangling play in SQream's architecture?

welcome_message:

speaker: assistant
message:
Data preprocessing and wrangling play a critical role in transforming raw data into a "clean" format to train machine learning algorithms. SQream's architecture leverages features such as fine-grained, low-overhead zone maps and data skipping to facilitate rapid and efficient analysis of large datasets, especially use cases that require multiple JOIN clauses and aggregations. This ensures optimal efficiency in analytics.

speaker: user
message: What is the difference between a data warehouse and a data lake?

welcome_message:
ðŸš€ Welcome to SQream! Leverage SQL on GPU to reduce analytics costs and increase performance!
Would you like to ask me about data challenges, watch a short demo or schedule a chat with our data solution experts? 
<sub>(To find more about our privacy policy, [click here](https://sqream.com/privacy-policy))</sub>
speaker: assistant
message:
A data warehouse stores historical data from various applications after the data has been filtered, organized, defined, and had metadata applied (i.e., schema-on-write). A data lake, on the other hand, is a repository that takes in the data as-is until needed for an analysis of some kind (i.e., schema-on-read). The data lakehouse aims to combine the best of both, ensuring new data imported into the lake conforms to a specific set of metadata conventions in open-table formats; however, the schema can automatically evolve over time. In a lakehouse, unlike in a typical data lake, the stored data can be queried directly on the lake, minimizing the need for copying data and making data governance easier. Data lakehouses also adopt reliability, consistency, access control and regulatory compliance best practices from data warehousing.

message: Using twins as "living laboratories" allows researchers to study the influence of genetic inheritance on various aspects of twins' lives. message:
eLSA is the flagship product of e-PORT, a Maritime Technology Startup based in Singapore. It is an AI-enabled 'Ship-in-Port' digital platform that offers real-time visibility and actionable data for cargo owners, terminals, carriers, agents, and port service providers. The goal of eLSA is to solve the "maritime darkspot" by providing direct, real-time, and relevant ship-in-port data to users, eliminating the need to chase for updates via email or phone.

eLSA aims to transition the traditional maritime supply chain into a digital ecosystem, reducing delays, waste, emissions, and costs through enhanced visibility. It is a modular platform made up of micro-apps that function independently to address individual pain points of key stakeholders, while also allowing seamless integration to address the larger issues of the industry.

The eLSA platform includes solutions for each specific stakeholder in the supply chain, such as Chartering Operating Systems, Voyage Management Systems, Ship Agency Operating Systems, and Port Service modules. It effectively bridges the gap between maintaining privacy and enabling real-time, error-free communication between stakeholders, protecting confidential information while ensuring crucial data reaches the right people when it needs to.

If you have any specific questions about eLSA, feel free to ask!

message: What is DCO?

welcome_message:
Hello! I'm agent aibot-openvpn.
I'm here to answer any questions you have, or maybe you'd rather choose a question others are asking me?
[more about me >](action/profile)
speaker: assistant
message:
DCO stands for Data Channel Offload. It is a technology that improves data speeds in OpenVPN connections. With DCO, the operating system handles the traffic using a Windows for DCO driver, reducing the workload and possible bottlenecks. DCO is supported in OpenVPN Connect 3.4 and newer on Windows, Access Server 2.12 and newer, and OpenVPN 2.6.0 and newer. DCO can be enabled separately on the client side as well. 

Source: [OpenVPN DCO Documentation](https://openvpn.net/documentation/openvpn-connect/openvpn-connect-3-4-release-notes/#dco)

message: How can I fix an issue with reaching the VPN server, Access Server?

welcome_message:
Hello! I'm agent aibot-openvpn.
I'm here to answer any questions you have, or maybe you'd rather choose a question others are asking me?
[more about me >](action/profile)
speaker: assistant
message:
If you're experiencing issues with reaching the VPN server (Access Server), there are several troubleshooting steps you can take:

1. Verify that the VPN server address resolves correctly: Ensure that the DNS record for the server's hostname resolves to the correct public IP address. You can use an online DNS checker tool to verify the status of the DNS record.

2. Check if you can reach the server by its IP address: Try accessing the Access Server web interface directly using the server's public IP address in your web browser.

3. Confirm that the server is still on the same IP address: Check if the server's public IP address has changed. If it has, update the DNS record or the Hostname/IP address setting in the Admin Web UI of the Access Server.

4. Verify that the server is alive: Ping the server's IP address to test network connectivity. If you can't reach the server via ping and the previous troubleshooting steps failed, it may indicate that the server or its network connection is down.

5. Try accessing the server via SSH: Use SSH to connect to the server's IP address and see if you get a response. If you can establish an SSH connection, it indicates that the server is up and running.

If the issue persists after trying these steps, consider updating your OS and the Access Server to the latest versions. If the problem still persists, it's recommended to contact the support team for further assistance.

Source: [Troubleshooting An OpenVPN Access Server Failure](https://openvpn.net/vpn-server-resources/troubleshooting-an-openvpn-access-server-failure/)

To fix issues with your VPN server and a persistent connection, you can try the following steps:

1. Restart your VPN server: Sometimes, a simple restart can resolve temporary issues. If the problem persists after a restart, proceed to the next steps.

2. Update your operating system and Access Server: Ensure that both your operating system and Access Server are up to date. Updates often include bug fixes and improvements that can help resolve connection issues.

3. Verify the VPN server address: Check if the VPN server address resolves correctly. Use a custom hostname that resolves to the public IP address of your Access Server. You can use an online DNS checker tool to verify the status of the DNS record.

4. Check connectivity using IP address: Try accessing the OpenVPN Access Server web interface directly using the server's public IP address in your web browser. This helps determine if there are any issues with DNS records.

5. Confirm server IP address: Ensure that your server is still on the expected IP address. If it has changed, update the DNS record or the Hostname/IP address setting in the Admin Web UI of the Access Server.

If the issue persists after following these steps, it is recommended to contact the support team for further assistance.

For more information, you can refer to the [Troubleshooting An OpenVPN Access Server Failure](https://openvpn.net/vpn-server-resources/troubleshooting-an-openvpn-access-server-failure/) documentation.

[source](https://openvpn.net/vpn-server-resources/troubleshooting-an-openvpn-access-server-failure/)

message: How do I uninstall Access Server?

welcome_message:
Hello! I'm agent aibot-openvpn.
I'm here to answer any questions you have, or maybe you'd rather choose a question others are asking me?
[more about me >](action/profile)
speaker: assistant
message:
To uninstall Access Server, you can follow these steps:

1. Remove the Access Server package from your operating system. The specific command may vary depending on your OS. For example, on Ubuntu, you can use the following command:
```
sudo apt-get remove openvpnas
```

2. Delete the Access Server configuration files. The location of these files may vary depending on your OS. For example, on Ubuntu, you can use the following command:
```
sudo rm -rf /usr/local/openvpn_as
```

3. Restart your system to ensure that all Access Server processes are stopped.

Please note that uninstalling Access Server will remove the software from your system, but it will not deactivate any subscription or stop any billing associated with the subscription. To stop using a subscription, you need to follow the steps outlined in the Access Server licensing portal on the OpenVPN website.

For more information, you can refer to the [Configuration Database Management And Backups](https://openvpn.net/vpn-server-resources/configuration-database-management-and-backups/) documentation.

welcome_message:
Hello! I'm agent cyber-internal.
I'm here to answer any questions you have, or maybe you'd rather choose a question others are asking me?
[more about me >](action/profile)
speaker: assistant
message:
Organizations are facing several challenges in relation to APIs. According to the documentation, some of these challenges include:

1. Standardization and consolidation: Large organizations often operate in isolated silos, and one recurring challenge is the need for standardization of tools and the consolidation of platforms and runtimes.

2. Growing complexity: APIs come in various types such as Rest, GraphQL, AsyncAPI, gRPC, SOAP, and others. The growing complexity of APIs poses a challenge for organizations in terms of design, development, integration, and management.

3. Collaboration and communication: APIs facilitate seamless communication among various cloud applications and platforms. However, organizations may face challenges in achieving improved collaboration and automated workflows due to disconnected systems and information silos.

4. API security risks: The urgency of API security is underscored by the findings from a survey mentioned in the documentation. Organizations have reported API-related breaches, with DDoS attacks being the primary attack vector. Many organizations struggle to understand the unique context of APIs and doubt the effectiveness of traditional security solutions in distinguishing genuine from fraudulent API activity.

5. API sprawl and inventory management: Organizations are grappling with challenges like API sprawl and keeping an accurate inventory of their APIs. They may have numerous third-party API connections, and managing these connections while ensuring security can be a daunting task.

These challenges highlight the need for organizations to address API-related risks, enhance collaboration, and implement effective security measures to protect their systems and data.

message:
Natural Language Processing (NLP) is the branch of Artificial Intelligence that gives machines the ability to read, understand and derive meaning from human languages. NLP combines techniques from fields such as linguistics and computer science to decipher language structure in order to create models that can comprehend and separate significant details from text and speech.

There are many steps when it comes to Natural Language Processing, and here are a couple: letâ€™s say you start with an article:

First, we break down the article into meaningful sentences or topics, this is called segmentation. Then we break down the text into tokens and explain each individual word to the computer which is called tokenization. Next, we do a technique called stemming, which is used to extract a wordâ€™s origin by removing prefixes, affixes, and suffixes. Now, we group together different inflected forms of a word by removing the wordâ€™s relation to gender, time, or mood- this is called lemmatization.

message: What challenges are organizations facing in relation to APIs?

welcome_message:
Hello! I'm agent cyber-internal.
I'm here to answer any questions you have, or maybe you'd rather choose a question others are asking me?
[more about me >](action/profile)
speaker: assistant
message:
Organizations are facing several challenges in relation to APIs. According to the documentation, some of these challenges include:

1. Standardization and consolidation: Large organizations often operate in isolated silos, and one recurring challenge is the need for standardization of tools and the consolidation of platforms and runtimes.

2. Growing complexity: APIs come in various types such as Rest, GraphQL, AsyncAPI, gRPC, SOAP, and others. The growing complexity of APIs poses a challenge for organizations in terms of design, development, integration, and management.

3. Collaboration and communication: APIs facilitate seamless communication among various cloud applications and platforms. However, organizations may face challenges in achieving improved collaboration and automated workflows due to disconnected systems and information silos.

4. API security risks: The urgency of API security is underscored by the findings from a survey mentioned in the documentation. Organizations have reported API-related breaches, with DDoS attacks being the primary attack vector. Many organizations struggle to understand the unique context of APIs and doubt the effectiveness of traditional security solutions in distinguishing genuine from fraudulent API activity.

5. API sprawl and inventory management: Organizations are grappling with challenges like API sprawl and keeping an accurate inventory of their APIs. They may have numerous third-party API connections, and managing these connections while ensuring security can be a daunting task.

These challenges highlight the need for organizations to address API-related risks, enhance collaboration, and implement effective security measures to protect their systems and data.

message: what is a SIEM exactly?

welcome_message: Hello! I'm the cybersecurity-brainiac.  I am trained to provide information on a wide range of infosec subjects from reading all 12 years of Cyber Defense Magazine (16,500+ pages of content). Sponsored this month by ![UnknownCyber](https://www.cyberdefensemagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unknowncyber.jpg) [UnknownCyber](https://www.unknowncyber.com/), the market leader of zero day malware detection.
speaker: assistant
message: According to the documentation, a SIEM stands for Security Information and Event Management. It is a technology that aggregates event data produced by security devices, network infrastructure, systems, and applications. The primary data source for SIEM is log data, but it can also process other forms of data, such as network telemetry. SIEM technology analyzes event data in real-time for early detection of targeted attacks and data breaches, and it collects, stores, investigates, and reports on log data for incident response, forensics, and regulatory compliance. SIEM systems provide real-time analysis of events for security monitoring, query and long-range analytics for historical analysis, and support for incident investigation and management.

message:
To set an expiration date for a pay link, follow these steps:

1. Set up your pay link by entering a name, price, and description.
2. Click on "Open settings" and enable the "Set an expiration date" toggle.
3. Choose a date when the link will expire and cannot be used.
4. Click "Create Link" to create the pay link with the expiration date.

For more information, you can refer to the [Wix Pay Links: Creating and Managing Pay Links](https://Wix.com) documentation.

message: Heirs' property refers to a type of property ownership where multiple heirs inherit an undivided interest in the property. It commonly occurs when a person passes away without a will or estate plan, and the property is inherited by their heirs. In heirs' property, each heir has a fractional share of ownership, and they collectively own the property as tenants in common. This type of ownership can lead to challenges and complexities in managing and transferring the property.

2. Teleprompter: BIGVU's teleprompter feature lets you view your script while recording, helping you speak confidently on camera. You can customize the speed and font size to match your natural pace.

6. Social Media Scheduling: With one tap, you can schedule and post your video across all your social media channels.

These are just some of the top must-know features of BIGVU.

welcome_message:

speaker: assistant
message:
The properties and specificity of each source of B-galactosidase significantly differ. The choice of suitable B-galactosidase source depends on the reaction conditions of lactose hydrolysis. Here are some key points:

1. Microbial Sources: B-galactosidase occurs in a variety of microorganisms, including yeasts, fungi, bacteria, and actinomycetes.

2. Dairy Yeasts: Dairy yeasts with a pH optimum of 6.5-7 are habitually used for the hydrolysis of lactose in milk or sweet whey.

3. Fungal B-galactosidases: Fungal B-galactosidases with an optimum pH of 3-5 are more suited for acidic whey hydrolysis.

4. Activity and Ions: The activity of different B-galactosidases also depends on the presence of ions. Fungal B-galactosidases are active without ions as cofactors, while yeast B-galactosidase isolated from Kluyveromyces lactis requires ions such as Mn2+, Na+, and B-galactosidase from Kluyveromyces fragilis requires ions such as Mn2+, Mg2+, K+. However, Ca2+ and heavy metals inhibit the enzyme activity of all B-galactosidases.

These are just some of the factors that determine the properties and specificity of each source of B-galactosidase. For more detailed information, please refer to the documentation.

welcome_message:

message:
Susu fermentasi memiliki beberapa manfaat bagi tubuh. Fermentasi adalah proses di mana mikroorganisme seperti bakteri atau ragi digunakan untuk mengubah susu menjadi produk yang lebih bermanfaat. Beberapa manfaat susu fermentasi antara lain:

1. Meningkatkan pencernaan: Susu fermentasi mengandung bakteri baik yang dapat membantu meningkatkan kesehatan saluran pencernaan. Bakteri ini membantu mencerna laktosa (gula dalam susu) dan membuatnya lebih mudah dicerna oleh tubuh.

2. Meningkatkan sistem kekebalan tubuh: Susu fermentasi mengandung probiotik, yaitu mikroorganisme hidup yang bermanfaat bagi kesehatan. Probiotik dapat membantu meningkatkan sistem kekebalan tubuh dan melindungi tubuh dari infeksi.

3. Meningkatkan penyerapan nutrisi: Fermentasi dapat meningkatkan ketersediaan nutrisi dalam susu. Misalnya, fermentasi dapat meningkatkan ketersediaan zat besi dalam susu, yang penting untuk pembentukan sel darah merah dan fungsi sistem kekebalan tubuh.

4. Mengurangi intoleransi laktosa: Bagi orang yang mengalami intoleransi laktosa, susu fermentasi dapat menjadi alternatif yang lebih mudah dicerna. Proses fermentasi mengubah laktosa menjadi asam laktat, sehingga mengurangi kadar laktosa dalam susu.

5. Meningkatkan kesehatan saluran pencernaan: Susu fermentasi dapat membantu menjaga keseimbangan bakteri baik dalam saluran pencernaan. Ini dapat membantu mengurangi risiko gangguan pencernaan seperti diare dan sembelit.

Namun, penting untuk diingat bahwa manfaat susu fermentasi dapat bervariasi tergantung pada jenis dan merek produk yang digunakan. Selalu periksa label produk dan konsultasikan dengan ahli gizi atau dokter jika Anda memiliki kondisi kesehatan tertentu.

welcome_message:

speaker: assistant
message:
Ada dua metode proses dekafeinasi yang umum digunakan, yaitu dekafeinasi dengan air dan dekafeinasi dengan pelarut. 

Metode dekafeinasi dengan air, seperti Swiss Water dan French Water decaffeination, didasarkan pada kelarutan kafein dalam air yang bergantung pada suhu. Proses ini melibatkan perendaman biji kopi dalam air panas, yang menyebabkan kafein dan zat-zat rasa larut dalam air. Untuk menghindari kehilangan rasa, biji kopi yang diekstraksi kemudian disemprot dengan air yang mengandung zat rasa, sehingga biji kopi dapat menyerap kembali zat rasa tersebut.

Metode dekafeinasi dengan pelarut didasarkan pada kelarutan kafein dalam pelarut organik seperti metilen klorida, etil asetat, etil alkohol, aseton, dan eter etil. Proses ini dapat dilakukan dengan ekstraksi langsung biji kopi menggunakan pelarut, atau dengan ekstraksi biji kopi menggunakan air terlebih dahulu, kemudian dilanjutkan dengan ekstraksi kafein dari ekstrak air menggunakan pelarut. Metode ini memungkinkan kafein dihilangkan dengan lebih efisien, tetapi menggunakan bahan kimia yang dapat memiliki efek negatif dan biaya yang tinggi.

Perbedaan utama antara kedua metode ini adalah dalam cara kafein dihilangkan dari biji kopi. Metode dekafeinasi dengan air menggunakan air sebagai pelarut utama, sementara metode dekafeinasi dengan pelarut menggunakan pelarut organik. Selain itu, metode dekafeinasi dengan air cenderung lebih aman dan ramah lingkungan karena tidak melibatkan bahan kimia berbahaya, sedangkan metode dekafeinasi dengan pelarut dapat memiliki risiko kesehatan dan dampak lingkungan yang lebih tinggi.

welcome_message:

I'm here to answer any questions you have, or maybe you'd rather choose a question others are asking me?
[more about me >](action/profile)
speaker: assistant
message:
To integrate Salesforce with TheySaid, you can follow these steps:

1. Create the custom object in Salesforce using the TheySaid XML file. This can be done by importing the XML file via the Workbench tool. The file contains all the necessary fields and relationships. Once imported, the custom object will be created in your Salesforce instance.

2. Create a new Salesforce profile that you will use for the integration service account. This profile will be granted access to the custom object during the setup process.

3. Create a service account or identify an existing Salesforce account that you want to use for integration purposes. Make sure this user is associated with the custom profile you created in step 2.

4. Enable pulse response and playbook sync in TheySaid settings. This can be done by clicking the cog icon in the lower-left corner of your TheySaid dashboard, selecting the Pulse Response and Playbook Sync box, and choosing the Salesforce tile. Log in with the admin account and select what you want to sync to your Salesforce account.

Once these steps are completed, Salesforce will be integrated with TheySaid, and you can take advantage of syncing pulse and playbook data between the two platforms.

[more about me >](action/profile)
speaker: assistant
message:
Sure! The schema for the location data is described in the Location Object. Here are the properties of the Location object:

- country_code: CiString(2) - ISO-3166 alpha-2 country code of the CPO that 'owns' this Location.
- party_id: CiString(3) - ID of the CPO that 'owns' this Location.
- id: CiString(36) - Uniquely identifies the location within the CPO's platform.
- publish: boolean - Defines if a Location may be published on a website or app.
- publish_allowed_to: PublishTokenType - This field may only be used when the publish field is set to false. Only owners of Tokens that match all the set fields of one PublishToken in the list are allowed to be shown this location.
- name: string(255) - Display name of the location.
- address: string(45) - Street/block name and house number if available.
- city: string(45) - City or town.
- postal_code: string(10) - Postal code of the location.
- country: string(3) - ISO 3166-1 alpha-3 code for the country of this location.
- coordinates: object - Coordinates of the location.
- parking_type: string - The general type of parking at the charge point location.
- evses: array - List of EVSEs that belong to this Location.
- directions: string - Human-readable directions on how to reach the location.
- operator_info: object - Information of the operator.
- suboperator_info: object - Information of the suboperator if available.
- owner_info: object - Information of the owner if available.
- facilities: array - Optional list of facilities this charging location directly belongs to.

Please note that this is just a summary of the schema. For more detailed information, you can refer to the Location Object section in the documentation.

welcome_message:

[more about me >](action/profile)
speaker: assistant
message:
Yes, as a household employer, you are required to pay household payroll taxes for a nanny, which may include Social Security & Medicare Taxes, Federal Unemployment Tax (FUTA), and state unemployment and disability insurance taxes. Occasionally, you or your employee may prefer to treat the worker as an "independent contractor," but this carries costly risks. Learn more about distinguishing a household employee from an independent contractor [here](https://www.homeworksolutions.com/knowledge-center/nanny-independent-contractor/).

message:
The Medicare tax pays for hospital insurance. Both you and your household employee may owe social security and Medicare taxes. Your share is 7.65% (6.2% for social security tax and 1.45% for Medicare tax) of the employee's social security and Medicare wages. Your employee's share is also 7.65% (6.2% for social security tax and 1.45% for Medicare tax). In addition to withholding Medicare tax at 1.45%, you must withhold a 0.9% Additional Medicare Tax from wages you pay to an employee in excess of $200,000 in a calendar year.

message: How do I clean the fiberglass

welcome_message:
Hello! I'm agent mattress-fiberglass-helper.
I'm here to answer any questions you have, or maybe you'd rather choose a question others are asking me?
[more about me >](action/profile)
speaker: assistant
message:
To clean fiberglass, you can follow these steps:

1. Thorough Cleaning: Use effective methods like a lint roller and a HEPA vacuum to capture fiberglass particles. Wipe down all hard surfaces with soap and water using a damp microfiber cloth or disposable damp cloth. Vacuum the affected areas multiple times using a vacuum cleaner with a high-efficiency particulate air (HEPA) or ultra-low penetration air (ULPA) filter.

2. Steam Cleaning: If you have carpets or upholstery that cannot be removed, steam cleaning them several times after vacuuming can help remove embedded fiberglass particles.

3. Air Out the Space: Open windows to increase natural ventilation and circulation. Use fans to improve air circulation and reduce the concentration of fiberglass particles in the air. Consider renting air scrubbers to purify and remove airborne contaminants, including fiberglass particles.

4. Proper Disposal and Personal Clean-up: Seal vacuum bags and used cleaning cloths in bags labeled as "contaminated" for appropriate disposal. Remove protective clothing without shaking or disturbing the fibers and place them in sealed bags. Wash lightly contaminated clothing separately in a washing machine with hot water.

Remember to take extra precautions to protect yourself from fiberglass exposure during the cleaning process and seek medical attention promptly if you experience any skin irritation or respiratory issues. It's also advisable to seek professional assistance if the fiberglass contamination is extensive or if you feel overwhelmed.

Hello! I'm agent shrinksense.

[more about me >](action/profile)
speaker: assistant
message: Shrinkflation is a gradual price inflation that affects consumers by reducing the quantity of a product for the same price. It is a phenomenon where instead of a rise in the price of a good or service, there is a decrease in the quantity of the product. This means that consumers end up paying more for less. Shrinkflation can be seen as a form of inflation hiding in plain sight, as it can go unnoticed until consumers realize they are getting less for their money.

speaker: assistant
message: One concept from the No-Code Playbook is the principle of minimizing the complexity of your overall solution architecture by adopting a primary architecture of no-code. This means that whenever possible, you should develop your applications using no-code tools. By doing so, you can efficiently capture the requirements and design visually, such as the user interface layout, business process flows, and business logic. This approach allows for a more direct and effective way to review and gather feedback from stakeholders and end users. It also eliminates the need for maintaining separate specifications and application code, as the no-code platform synchronizes the specification and the working application throughout the lifecycle. This principle helps improve the efficiency and accuracy of the development process, resulting in higher quality feedback and a more aligned solution architecture.

message: What is the Kanban methodology, per the NCP?

welcome_message:
Hello! I'm agent citizen-dev-assistant.
I'm here to answer any questions you have, or maybe you'd rather choose a question others are asking me?
[more about me >](action/profile)
speaker: assistant
message: The NCP documentation describes the Kanban methodology as a "just-in-time" approach to managing complex workflows. It originated from lean manufacturing and is commonly used in modern Agile software development. Kanban involves breaking down work into "cards" and "columns" on visual boards, such as "requested," "in-progress," and "done." It allows teams to easily track and communicate updates, provides visibility into scope and progress, and facilitates collaboration and discussion about priorities. Kanban is recommended over Scrum for no-code development due to its continuous delivery model, flexibility, and ease of adoption by business teams.
